<bibRefCitation author="Smith, C. E." box="[743,1154,964,990]" pageId="4" pageNumber="53" pagination="1 - 114" refId="ref4352" refString="Smith, C. E. (1954) The New World species of Sloanea (Elaeocarpaceae). Contributions from the Gray Herbarium of Harvard University 175: 1 - 114." type="journal article" year="1954">—BRAZIL. Amazonas: Manaus</bibRefCitation>
