<subSubSection pageId="4" pageNumber="53" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="4.[151,1436,925,1183]" pageId="4" pageNumber="53">
Smith (1954: 86
<typeStatus box="[395,404,1041,1067]" pageId="4" pageNumber="53">)</typeStatus>
indicated as “Type collection” the specimen 
<bibRefCitation author="McNeill, J. &amp; Barrie, F. R. &amp; Burdet, H. M. &amp; Demoulin, V. &amp; Hawksworth, D. L. &amp; Marhold, K. &amp; Nicolson, D. H. &amp; Prado, J. &amp; Silva, P. C. &amp; Skog, J. E. &amp; Wiersema, J. H. &amp; Turland, N. J." box="[953,1236,1041,1067]" pageId="4" pageNumber="53" refId="ref4108" refString="McNeill, J., Barrie, F. R., Burdet, H. M., Demoulin, V., Hawksworth, D. L., Marhold, K., Nicolson, D. H., Prado, J., Silva, P. C., Skog, J. E., Wiersema, J. H. &amp; Turland, N. J. (eds.) (2006) International Code of Botanical Nomenclature (Vienna Code). Adopted by the Seventeenth International Botanical Congress Vienna, Austria, July 2005. Regnum Vegetabile 146. Gantner, Ruggell, Liechtenstein. 568 pp." type="book" year="2006">
A
<emphasis box="[978,1150,1041,1067]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="53">. Ducke HJBR</emphasis>
25113
</bibRefCitation>
. However, as he attests, materials collected 
<typeStatus box="[469,498,1080,1106]" pageId="4" pageNumber="53">on</typeStatus>
different 
<typeStatus box="[615,740,1080,1106]" isOtherTypeStatus="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="53">dates were</typeStatus>
put together on the same sheet and 
<emphasis box="[1166,1259,1080,1106]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="53">thus are</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Ducke, A." pageId="4" pageNumber="53" pagination="1 - 281" refId="ref3602" refString="Ducke, A. (1922) Plantes Nouvelles ou peu connues de la region amazonienne. II Serie. Archivos do Jardim Botanico do Rio de Janeiro 3: 1 - 281." type="journal article" year="1922">not suitable as lectotypes (Art</bibRefCitation>
. 8.2 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[399,470,1118,1144]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="53">of the</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Martius, C. F. P. von" box="[480,741,1118,1144]" pageId="4" pageNumber="53" pagination="33 - 48" refId="ref4085" refString="Martius, C. F. P. von (1841) Herbarium florae brasiliensis. Flora 24: 33 - 48." type="journal article" year="1841">ICNB, McNeill et al.</bibRefCitation>
2006
<emphasis box="[817,826,1118,1144]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="53">)</emphasis>
. This way
<typeStatus box="[953,958,1118,1144]" pageId="4" pageNumber="53">,</typeStatus>
we have chosen as lectotype the 
<collectingCountry box="[1373,1436,1118,1144]" name="Brazil" pageId="4" pageNumber="53">other</collectingCountry>
material 
<collectingRegion box="[254,311,1157,1183]" country="Brazil" name="Para" pageId="4" pageNumber="53">cited</collectingRegion>
by 
<collectorName box="[355,647,1157,1183]" pageId="4" pageNumber="53">Ducke in the protologue.</collectorName>
</paragraph>
